QuestData.Title: Molted Spineshell
QuestData.Description:
<The molted shell of a defeated spine crab, a vicious species of crab first encountered in Nazjatar.
The spines that stick out from it are quite sharp.
Artisan Itanu may have some use for this.>
QuestData.LogDescription: Show the Molted Spineshell to Artisan Itanu in Mezzamere in Nazjatar.
